927
01:05:27,000 --> 01:05:28,250
They're actually calling us.

928
01:05:31,240 --> 01:05:32,360
Hello, Dad?

929
01:05:32,780 --> 01:05:33,790
You finished the video?

930
01:05:33,960 --> 01:05:34,640
Mm...

931
01:05:34,680 --> 01:05:36,000
We're pretty free, alright?

932
01:05:36,160 --> 01:05:39,320
Mami made me watch it,
so I had no choice.

933
01:05:39,600 --> 01:05:40,320
By the way...

934
01:05:40,640 --> 01:05:42,580
Dad, Duang is right here.
Do you want to talk to him?

935
