Turn on the speaker!
I can't hear them clearly.

936
01:05:46,880 --> 01:05:47,960
Hello, Duang?

937
01:05:48,160 --> 01:05:49,520
Hello, Mami?

938
01:05:49,560 --> 01:05:51,680
How did I do?

939
01:05:51,880 --> 01:05:54,520
Duang! You knocked it out of the park.

940
01:05:54,560 --> 01:05:56,640
You danced well, and your moves were so tight.

941
01:05:56,680 --> 01:05:58,120
You blew everyone out of the water.

942
01:05:58,160 --> 01:06:00,360
You stood out the most on the stage.
Do you know that?

943
01:06:00,400 --> 01:06:01,670
Come on, Mami!

944
01:06:01,960 --> 01:06:03,640
That's too much praise.

945
01:06:03,680 --> 01:06:05,560
Come on, it's not.

946
01:06:05,760 --> 01:06:07,360
