950
01:06:14,120 --> 01:06:15,280
I mean, what is it called?

951
01:06:15,320 --> 01:06:17,320
The term is "T-pop artist," right?

952
01:06:17,830 --> 01:06:18,510
Oh?

953
01:06:18,600 --> 01:06:19,770
How do you know that?

954
01:06:19,810 --> 01:06:20,690
Come on!

955
01:06:20,730 --> 01:06:24,390
You barely put your effort into anything,
so I did some research.

956
01:06:24,560 --> 01:06:27,320
Do you know that I really wanted to be there,
but you didn't invite me?

957
01:06:27,360 --> 01:06:30,150
Or else both of us would be right at the front.

958
01:06:30,190 --> 01:06:30,760
Mm.

959
01:06:30,800 --> 01:06:32,110
