960
01:06:32,240 --> 01:06:33,320
You'd embarrass me.

961
01:06:33,360 --> 01:06:34,960
This already delights me.

962
01:06:35,720 --> 01:06:36,520
Embarrass?

963
01:06:36,560 --> 01:06:38,720
How? You're embarrassed by my love?

964
01:06:38,760 --> 01:06:40,170
I'm upset, you know?

965
01:06:40,920 --> 01:06:42,320
Mami, I'm sorry.

966
01:06:42,600 --> 01:06:43,750
Come on, Mami.

967
01:06:44,000 --> 01:06:45,360
I've sent you all of the videos.

968
01:06:45,640 --> 01:06:46,910
Stop being so grumpy.

969
01:06:48,080 --> 01:06:48,690
Duang.

970
01:06:48,880 --> 01:06:50,320
Jamie and Pae asked you for photos.

971
01:06:51,520 --> 01:06:52,280
Duang.

972
01:06:52,660 --> 01:06:53,640
Your friend's calling.

973
01:06:54,230 --> 01:06:56,030
Tell Dad we'll talk to him later
when we're home.

974
01:06:57,480 --> 01:06:59,120
We'll talk to you soon, Dad.

975
01:06:59,160 --> 01:07:00,040
- Right.
- Alright.

976
01:07:01,280 --> 01:07:01,920
Dad, play them.

977
01:07:01,960 --> 01:07:02,360
Huh?

978
01:07:02,400 --> 01:07:03,520
- The videos!
- Again?

979
01:07:03,560 --> 01:07:04,280
One more.

980
01:07:04,320 --> 01:07:05,330
