Curse you, Funan!

994
01:07:32,520 --> 01:07:34,520
You messed up my hair!

995
01:07:39,080 --> 01:07:41,320
Hey, can you fix my hair?

996
01:07:43,400 --> 01:07:44,000
Oh.

997
01:07:44,960 --> 01:07:45,760
It's okay.

998
01:07:45,800 --> 01:07:47,880
I'll fix it myself.

999
