Mm.

1002
01:08:11,910 --> 01:08:15,520
Are you so flustered that you changed the topic?

1003
01:08:15,760 --> 01:08:16,399
Wait...

1004
01:08:16,920 --> 01:08:18,399
Where did you get the bouquet of sunflowers?

1005
01:08:21,640 --> 01:08:22,560
It's from my family.

1006
01:08:23,359 --> 01:08:25,050
You've also got a lovely family.

1007
01:08:26,600 --> 01:08:27,609
Not as lovely as yours.

1008
01:08:32,720 --> 01:08:34,109
Come on. Group photo time.

1009
01:08:56,319 --> 01:08:58,319
