1028
01:09:56,870 --> 01:09:58,430
I just think I still could've done it better.

1029
01:10:03,670 --> 01:10:04,670
Well...

1030
01:10:07,520 --> 01:10:09,240
I'll always have your back.

1031
01:10:13,160 --> 01:10:14,170
Do you think,

1032
