1047
01:11:47,320 --> 01:11:48,920
It's an important Story.

1048
01:11:50,560 --> 01:11:52,060
So I want to treasure it while I can.

1049
01:12:20,030 --> 01:12:21,230
Hey...

1050
01:12:26,320 --> 01:12:27,640
