1054
01:13:02,040 --> 01:13:03,640
Feeling better now?

1055
01:13:07,800 --> 01:13:08,890
Just a little longer.

1056
01:13:14,840 --> 01:13:16,260
You're such a tease.

1057
01:13:18,520 --> 01:13:19,720
Be patient.

1058
01:13:46,280 --> 01:13:47,600
Shall we take this more seriously?

1059
01:13:56,880 --> 01:13:57,760
Huh?

1060
01:13:58,520 --> 01:13:59,720
