1061
01:13:59,880 --> 01:14:00,930
What?

1062
01:14:01,850 --> 01:14:02,850
Like...

1063
01:14:05,600 --> 01:14:07,800
Like, let it be known that
I'm officially interested in you.

1064
01:14:09,880 --> 01:14:10,880
Okay?

1065
01:14:22,360 --> 01:14:23,360
That's great.

1066
01:14:24,160 --> 01:14:25,160
That's excellent.

1067
01:15:07,480 --> 01:15:10,480
♫It might be the first day
that you found the clue♫

1068
01:15:10,840 --> 01:15:13,840
♫But it won't be the only day I'd love you♫

1069
01:15:14,140 --> 01:15:18,120
♫No matter when, I'll always be sure♫

1070
01:15:18,320 --> 01:15:21,320
♫That it's you♫

1071
01:15:25,480 --> 01:15:29,880
♫Simply understand
everything with your heart♫

1072
01:15:30,520 --> 01:15:33,120
♫And you'll see more than♫

1073
01:15:33,520 --> 01:15:36,930
♫What you've asked♫

1074
01:15:39,000 --> 01:15:43,600
♫Let your heart guide your way♫

1075
01:15:44,080 --> 01:15:46,880
♫Can you hear what it says?♫

1076
01:15:50,320 --> 01:15:53,920
♫It had to be you♫

1077
01:15:54,680 --> 01:15:57,280
♫You♫

1078
01:15:57,660 --> 01:16:01,390
♫You're the first to ever make me feel this way♫

1079
01:16:01,430 --> 01:16:03,880
♫It's you, the one and only♫

1080
01:16:03,920 --> 01:16:07,320
♫It had to be you♫

1081
01:16:08,190 --> 01:16:10,800
♫You♫

1082
01:16:10,840 --> 01:16:14,560
